  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 350 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Butter each slice of bread on both sides.",
    "Place the bread slices on a baking sheet.",
    "Sprinkle shredded cheese over the bread slices.",
    "Add paprika, salt, black pepper, and garlic powder on top of the cheese.",
    "Drizzle water over the cheese and spices.",
    "Bake in the preheated oven for 10 minutes or until the cheese is melted and fluffy.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for a minute or two.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
